Author: brookeD95
Text: I feel you on this one. I will go days on end barely eating enough for a small child...  Then my brain is like: "Yo maybe if you eat a healthy, well rounded lunch today you'll feel better and realize that restricting is dumb"  Me: "Wow I actually feel like a real human person!"  Also me: \*adds everything into MFP and has a mini heart attack over consuming *450* calories in one meal\*
